# --- OpenStrata / build state (tool-owned, never committed) ---
/build/
**/build/
**/dist/
/.strata/
**/.strata/
CMakeUserPresets.json
strata.lock

# Built plugin libraries are staged into each bundle's lib/ by `ost plugin build`.
**/lib/

# --- Docs ---
# /docs is tracked by default. It was local-by-default while the ost dogfooding
# reports under docs/report/ost/ were unpublished; those reports are now a
# deliberate artifact of this project (docs/reports/ost/), so the exclusion and
# its negation list are gone. Keep machine-specific scratch under /docs/local/.
/docs/local/

# Local samples and experiments.
/scratch/

# --- CMake / MSVC generated ---
CMakeCache.txt
CMakeFiles/
cmake_install.cmake
CTestTestfile.cmake
*.obj
*.pdb
*.ilk
*.exp
*.lib
*.dll

# --- Python cache ---
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo

# --- Editor / OS noise ---
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# --- Agent / assistant tooling (local, not shared) ---
/.claude/
